### Key Scaling Decisions

| Concern | Solution |
|---|---|
| Connection routing | Sticky sessions by document ID |
| Cross-server sync | Redis Pub/Sub for real-time events |
| Hot documents | Dedicated server instances |
| Storage scaling | Sharding by document ID |
| Operation history | Cassandra for time-series data |
| Snapshots | Periodic compaction every 100 ops |

